citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 3:10pm on Tuesday,
December 5, 2023. The inspector knocked on the door and called the phone number on file. The licensee answered but
stated was not available for an inspection.
End Section
